      <italic class="italic">Citrus reticulata</italic> L.
     </bold>
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">370 Mbp (
     <xref rid="B262" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">Wang L. et al., 2018</xref>)
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Accessible from: 
     <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://www.citrusgenomedb.org/organism/5941" class="ext-link" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">https://www.citrusgenomedb.org/organism/5941</ext-link> or GenBank taxa id: 85571
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td"/>
   </tr>
   <tr class="tr">
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">
     <bold class="bold">
      <italic class="italic">Citrus medica Citrus maxima Citrus ichangensis</italic>
     </bold>
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">407 Mbp, 380 Mbp, 391 Mbp (
     <xref rid="B261" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">Wang X. et al., 2017</xref>; 
