    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Accessible from: 
     <italic class="italic">C. medica</italic>
     <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://www.citrusgenomedb.org/organism/5945" class="ext-link" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">https://www.citrusgenomedb.org/organism/5945</ext-link> or GenBank taxa id: 171251 
     <italic class="italic">C. maxima</italic>
     <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://www.citrusgenomedb.org/organism/5947" class="ext-link" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">https://www.citrusgenomedb.org/organism/5947</ext-link> or GenBank taxa id: 37334 
     <italic class="italic">C. ichangensis</italic>
