     <bold class="bold">
      <italic class="italic">Citrus unshiu</italic> L.
     </bold>
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">370 Mbp (
     <xref rid="B236" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">Shimizu et al., 2017</xref>)
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Accessible from: 
     <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.citrusgenome.jp/" class="ext-link" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">http://www.citrusgenome.jp/</ext-link> or GenBank taxa id: 55188
