      <italic class="italic">Olea europaea</italic> L
     </bold>
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">1380 Mbp (
     <xref rid="B68" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">Cruz et al., 2016</xref>; 
     <xref rid="B253" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">Unver et al., 2017</xref>)
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Accessible from subsp. europeae GenBank taxa id: 4146 subsp. sylvestris 
