    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">• Olive Genetic Diversity Database (OGDD) (
     <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.bioinfo-cbs.org/ogdd/" class="ext-link" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">http://www.bioinfo-cbs.org/ogdd/</ext-link>), a genetic, morphologic and chemical database of worldwide olive oil production for the identification of unknown olive tree cultivars, based on SSR markers (
